content: Hi, I believed that I completed my shadow debriefing form and I was wondering how do I gain access to the chat captain team?

Hi <@795513525375991818> - Thank you for your leadership in multiple areas. Just in case, I am going to DM you the shadow debrief form. In my experience helping a few folks, some people get the regular phone bank form and the shadow form confused as they are similar. I do not see KC permissions added yet, so there may just be a delay in getting your debrief form processed.  Will check in via DM shortly.  Thanks again, Jay
Hi Frank--you should have access to the KC channels now
